code: /**  * Handle a STOMP frame with the payload converted to the target type returned  * from {@link #getPayloadType(StompHeaders)}.  * @param headers the headers of the frame  * @param payload the payload, or {@code null} if there was no payload  */ void handleFrame(StompHeaders headers, @Nullable Object payload).
